ã       ããã parse.ts                               # parser impl
ã       ããã __tests__/
ã           ããã parse.test.ts                      # unit tests for parser
ã           ããã fixtures/                          # canonical jsonl samples
ããã conversations/
ã   ããã src/
ã       ããã plugin.ts                              # MODIFIED ã chat:turn-end no longer calls appendTurn (keep last_activity_at)
ã       ããã __tests__/                             # MODIFIED ã assertions on the new path
ããã channel-web/
    ããã (no source changes if Q1=(a); shape-compatible)
```

Plus: package.json deps in `conversations` add `@ax/agent-claude-sdk-runner-host` workspace dep.

---

## Bite-sized TDD tasks

Order: D-2 parser first (no other deps) ã D-3 conversations:get pivot ã D-1 drop appendTurn ã D-4 channel-web verify (no-op if shapes match) ã D-5 canary.

D-2 first because the parser is a pure function; can be unit-tested in isolation. D-3 next because it's the integration point. D-1 next so the write path stops adding to a now-unused table. D-4 verifies channel-web doesn't break. D-5 is the end-to-end canary.

### Task 1: Scaffold `@ax/agent-claude-sdk-runner-host`

