2. `package.json`: `name: "@ax/agent-claude-sdk-runner-host"`, `peerDependencies: { "@ax/core": "*" }`, `dependencies: { zod: "^3" }`.
3. `SECURITY.md`: minimal ã package is pure JSON parsing, no spawn, no network, no filesystem (caller passes bytes). Capability budget: zero.
