11. **set-title throws** ã `set-title` stub throws. Subscriber logs + swallows.

For the bus.fire pattern: look at how `packages/conversations/src/__tests__/subscribe.test.ts` triggers `chat:turn-end`. The bus typically has `fire(eventName, ctx, payload)` that returns once all subscribers complete.

